Armada Stream 40 - Best Of 2013 

                 Electro House, Trance | ARVA / Armada Music B.V.

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-12-13 | 02:19:23 | 322 Mb



Based on the weekly Armada Stream 40 list, Armada Music brings the 40 most popular tunes of the year in its 'Best of 2013' compilation. Ranked high in the charts, buzzing on social media and moving crowds in the clubs and at festivals, you'll find only the biggest hits of Armada's releases on this compilation. The pack includes the most essential tracks, by the likes of Armin van Buuren, W&W, Vicetone, Arty, Shogun, BT, Christian Burns and many more!
